  "instructions": [
    "preheat robata grill to 400°f (200°c).",
    "thread portobello mushrooms, zucchini, yellow squash, red bell pepper, and red onion onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "in a small bowl, whisk together golden syrup, kombu-cold-extract, and lemon juice.",
    "brush the skewers with olive oil and season with oregano, garlic, and salt.",
    "grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, or until the vegetables are tender and lightly charred."
  ],
